+## Constraints
+
+- Do not derive full reduced ODEs.
+- Do not score delayed-transfer windows or robustness.
+- Do not treat packet-role families as the search object.
+- Keep every classification claim at the first budget only.
+
+## Deliverables
+
+- `REPORT.md`
+- `REPORT-SUMMARY.md`
