+
+### Enlargement verdict
+
+- `[INFERRED]` The admissible enlargement does **not** reveal a hidden finite
+  exact fixed point.
+- `[INFERRED]` It confirms that the apparent six-wavevector pseudo-survivor was
+  an artifact of over-pruning the exact ledger.
+
+## Budget-Limited Verdict
+
+- `[INFERRED]` No genuinely invariant finite support survives at the first
+  budget.
+- `[INFERRED]` The sharpest earned current-budget obstruction is:
+
+  ```text
+  recursive closure spills outside the one-triad budget on every honest seed,
+  and the only tempting pseudo-survivor fails the admissible-enlargement audit.
+  ```
+
+- `[INFERRED]` Chain Step 3 is therefore **not** well posed on any first-budget
