+| --- | --- | --- | --- |
+| nondegenerate `(+++)` | `[INFERRED]` at minimum `±(p-q)`, `±(2p+q)`, `±(p+2q)` | `budget spill` | `[INFERRED]` mirror-complete off-orbit pairs force new wavevectors on the first honest pass |
