+- `[INFERRED]` After quotienting by conjugation,
+  global helical-sign relabeling,
+  and the `p <-> q` symmetry,
+  the raw sign triples reduce to three canonical classes for
+
+  ```text
+  (sigma_k, sigma_p, sigma_q):
+  ```
+
+  1. `(+++)`
+  2. `(++-)`
+  3. `(+--)`
