+| nondegenerate `(+--)` | `[INFERRED]` at minimum `±(p-q)`, `±(2p+q)`, `±(p+2q)` | `budget spill` | `[INFERRED]` same |
+
+- `[INFERRED]` No live seed reaches a genuine finite fixed point inside the
+  one-triad budget.
