+
+```text
+tau_0 = ((k, sigma_k), (p, sigma_p), (q, sigma_q)),
+k = p + q,
+p != q,
+p not parallel to q.
+```
+
+### Closure operations in order
+
+1. `[VERIFIED]` Add mandatory conjugates:
+
+   ```text
+   S_0 = { ±(k, sigma_k), ±(p, sigma_p), ±(q, sigma_q) }.
+   ```
+
+2. `[INFERRED]` Orbit-internal ordered pairs reproduce the seed orbit:
+
+   ```text
+   (p, q) -> k,
+   (k, -p) -> q,
+   (k, -q) -> p
+   ```
+
+   and their mirrors.
