+3. `[INFERRED]` Self-pairs do not rescue the budget:
+
+   ```text
+   Gamma_{r,p,p}(u)
+     = -i overline{u^(r)} · [ (p · u^(p)) P_r u^(p) ] = 0
+   ```
+
+   by divergence-free orthogonality, so the honest spill does not come from
