+### Closure-forced companions and spectators
+
+- `[VERIFIED]` Mandatory representation companions:
+  `-k`,
+  `-p`,
+  `-q`.
+- `[INFERRED]` First closure-forced spectator wavevector orbits:
+
+  ```text
+  ±(p - q),
+  ±(2p + q),
