+## Recursive Closure Ledger
+
+Take any live canonical seed
+
+```text
+tau_0 = ((k, sigma_k), (p, sigma_p), (q, sigma_q)),
+k = p + q,
+p != q,
+p not parallel to q.
+```
+
+### Closure operations in order
+
+1. `[VERIFIED]` Add mandatory conjugates:
